YOUR VESSEL FIRST.

114
00:08:08,822 --> 00:08:10,407
YOU CHOOSE, CAPTAIN.

115
00:08:10,531 --> 00:08:12,492
I'LL DESTROY
YOUR CONTROL PANEL.

116
00:08:21,918 --> 00:08:24,045
TAKE HIM TO SICK BAY.

117
00:08:24,171 --> 00:08:27,799
REVERSE COURSE.

118
00:08:27,924 --> 00:08:30,093
HEAD BACK
FOR TANTALUS COLONY.

119
00:08:35,474 --> 00:08:38,768
ABNORMAL, OF COURSE.

120
00:08:38,893 --> 00:08:40,687
IT'S NOT
SCHIZOPHRENIA...

121
00:08:40,812 --> 00:08:42,647
TISSUE DAMAGE...

122
00:08:42,772 --> 00:08:44,607
OR ANY CONDITION
I'M ACQUAINTED WITH, JIM.

123
00:08:44,732 --> 00:08:46,318
YOU KNOW,
AFTER GETTING HIM HERE,

124
00:08:46,443 --> 00:08:48,111
