A TRIPLE DOSE OF SEDATIVE
TO PUT HIM UNDER.

125
00:08:48,236 --> 00:08:50,030
THE REPORT SAID
HE WAS QUITE TALKATIVE.

126
00:08:50,155 --> 00:08:51,656
BUT NOT
VERY INFORMATIVE.

127
00:08:51,781 --> 00:08:53,533
HE CLAIMED ONE THING,
THEN HE SEEMED TO FORGET.

128
00:08:53,658 --> 00:08:56,036
AND THEN,
HE'D START TO CLAIM
SOMETHING ELSE.

129
00:08:56,161 --> 00:09:00,790
BUT ALWAYS WITH
JUST THE RING
OF TRUTH IN IT.

130
00:09:00,915 --> 00:09:02,876
I'D SURE LIKE TO
STUDY THIS ONE, JIM.

131
00:09:03,001 --> 00:09:06,129
IT'S NOT OUR PROBLEM,
BONES.

132
00:09:06,254 --> 00:09:09,508
YOU SMART,
BUTTON-PUSHING
BRASS HAT.

133
00:09:09,632 --> 00:09:10,717
WASH YOUR HANDS
OF IT.

134
00:09:10,842 --> 00:09:13,720
IS THAT YOUR SYSTEM?

135
00:09:13,845 --> 00:09:16,348
YOU'RE BOTH QUITE
SURE OF YOURSELVES,
AREN'T YOU?

136
00:09:16,473 --> 00:09:18,016
QUITE EXPERT.

137
00:09:18,933 --> 00:09:20,185
TAKE HIM BACK.

138
00:09:20,310 --> 00:09:22,145
LET SOMEONE ELSE
WORRY ABOUT HIM.

139
00:09:23,522 --> 00:09:25,315
