YOUR NAME WAS?

140
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,442
MY NAME?

141
00:09:28,943 --> 00:09:30,862
MY NAME IS--AAH--

142
00:09:33,990 --> 00:09:35,575
SIMON...

143
00:09:38,161 --> 00:09:40,580
VAN GELDER.

144
00:09:43,875 --> 00:09:45,460
I WAS THE DIRECTOR OF--

145
00:09:45,585 --> 00:09:47,379
[GROANS]

146
00:09:49,381 --> 00:09:50,590
DIRECTOR...

147
00:09:53,009 --> 00:09:54,594
AT THE...

148
00:09:54,719 --> 00:09:56,596
TANTALUS COLONY.

149
00:09:58,932 --> 00:09:59,849
YOU SEE WHAT I MEAN?

150
00:09:59,974 --> 00:10:02,810
I WAS A GRADUATE OF...

151
00:10:02,936 --> 00:10:04,979
OF...

152
00:10:05,105 --> 00:10:06,940
I WAS ASSISTANT TO...

153
00:10:07,065 --> 00:10:08,358
TO...

154
00:10:12,112 --> 00:10:14,364
DOCTOR...

155
00:10:14,489 --> 00:10:18,201
AAH!

156
00:10:18,326 --> 00:10:19,660
AAH...

157
00:10:22,705 --> 00:10:23,831
I KNEW...

158
00:10:23,957 --> 00:10:26,000
I KNEW.

159
00:10:27,544 --> 00:10:30,338
BUT
THEY'VE ERASED IT.

160
00:10:30,464 --> 00:10:33,216
ERASED?

161
00:10:33,341 --> 00:10:34,842
EDITED...

162
00:10:34,968 --> 00:10:37,220
ADJUSTED...

163
00:10:37,345 --> 00:10:39,097
SUBVERTED ME.

164
00:10:39,222 --> 00:10:40,974
BUT I WON'T FORGET!

165
00:10:41,099 --> 00:10:43,101
I WON'T FORGET!

166
00:10:43,226 --> 00:10:45,604
YOU...YOU'RE SO
BLIND IGNORANT.

167
00:10:45,728 --> 00:10:48,022
YOU BELIEVE I BELONG
BACK THERE, DON'T YOU?

168
00:10:48,148 --> 00:10:49,983
DEAD OR ALIVE.

169
00:10:50,108 --> 00:10:52,026
WELL, I WON'T LET YOU
TAKE ME BACK!

170
00:10:52,152 --> 00:10:53,612
I'M NOT GOING!

171
00:10:53,736 --> 00:10:55,572
I'LL DIE FIRST!

172
00:10:55,696 --> 00:10:56,739
DO YOU HEAR?

173
00:10:56,864 --> 00:10:57,782
I'M NOT GOING!

174
00:10:57,907 --> 00:10:59,618
NO!

175
00:10:59,742 --> 00:11:00,827
NO!

176
00:11:00,952 --> 00:11:02,954
NO...
[HYPOSPRAY HISSES]

177
00:11:16,426 --> 00:11:17,385
